Title: 800: A Transformative Century of Technological Progress, with Annie P.
Description:
The SuperDataScience Podcast is celebrating its 800th episode! Host Jon Krohn speaks to his grandmother, Annie, about growing up at a time when so many technologies we take for granted today were yet to be developed. Listen in to hear Annie’s experience of the changes in technology across 94 years and how she and her family fared in 1940s Ukraine with no electricity or running water.


Additional materials: www.superdatascience.com/800
